{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "8523fdb0-c6e6-42e1-9f37-d62fbbd1cdd9",
    "name": "I05: Aeolus in Love",
    "sceneId": "1c60250c-dab6-4aaa-aaeb-b7f4203ccb9d",
    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "533e3e35-6479-4e0a-a3fc-fab5d827f1f8",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "035d492c-b43c-4be8-9fa2-dcabd3732ebb",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "c8527fba-09e6-43b2-ad3d-2b8ad7f7f31e",
                            "text": "Ask About How Moira Became a Paladin",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "19bd840c-7c6f-4e2f-91ea-d257b753b830",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "amount": "1",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3c3cd0f3-21d8-4312-a019-4c0d46caa65a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "How did you become a Paladin? It doesn't seem like an easy job to get into.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "950462f2-537d-48e0-814b-7f2fbaf7e64d",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I once thought that Paladins were just the stuff of bards' songs and fairytales until the day that I met one. He was every bit my dream of a Paladin - kind, brave, and seeking justice for people he'd never even met.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "94d02c65-9c78-452a-8e2b-7a5a4e286ede",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I helped him when he was sorely hurt and near death. He told me that I, myself, was a Paladin even though I'd never lifted a sword in my life. He asked me to help him save others, and of course, I said yes.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f0c1807b-bef9-48f7-b36b-f1874b902d3c",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I would have followed him into Hades if he had asked me to.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "45b15b95-2882-4fc0-9880-399c2260089d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Did you love him?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "aae671de-e6c2-43f1-89c3-4ef976760c26",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That I did, with all my heart. Alas, he had already given his heart and hand to someone who was more worthy of his devotion than I will ever be.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "dc2a1e29-8bcc-4121-94d2-3995b814aff7",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I may not have found my one True Love, but I did gain a calling and a future unlike any that I had dreamed. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "10",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "0dc5ce0b-10a5-47ea-89ac-1deb17ea8712",
                            "text": "Talk About the School Thief",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "184d7548-80e1-41ae-b084-3d2e7ab2ddca",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "84e65657-53fe-48a1-b5ce-cc6248d4a418",
                                            "text": "Say Something Charming About Catching the School Thief",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "id": "2f9204cf-cd11-429e-8f39-f90185745ee5",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                                    "target": "34",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "a216ecae-f29f-45bf-add2-fc1b1ffb3aba",
                                                                "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                                "amount": "1",
                                                                "change": "1",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "6bcf9abc-a486-4836-b14e-4e84bc60333d",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                    "text": "Yes, I did catch the School Thief. I just wanted to bring him to justice and make certain that he did not steal again.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "0b21f537-c5dc-40fe-b485-70aafd1172b0",
                                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "That was very good of you, Shawn. Who knows, perhaps you, too, could be a Paladin someday.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "3",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "7a783cfc-5603-4a1f-8622-c59ee91d3c12",
                                            "text": "Say Something Clever About the School Thief",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "id": "3051063b-3b83-437b-899f-488427d41255",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                                    "target": "34",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "0edbe446-a759-45e7-b40c-58875e341622",
                                                                "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                                "amount": "1",
                                                                "change": "1",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "a45d8767-1cfa-4e5b-8712-4ee90b6fadb7",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                    "text": "I tracked down the School Thief because I wanted to show everyone that I really do belong here at the university - and that the Disbarred Bards can be heroes, too.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "c1326c73-1182-4446-be49-606a05f09434",
                                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "There's no doubt in my mind that you will be a great hero someday, Shawn.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "3",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "725c5bc7-0ba8-437e-a60a-b7fecc824d4e",
                                            "text": "Say Something Snarky About the School Thief",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "id": "1cde09b6-6f10-4da5-b329-78f502f0607c",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                                    "target": "34",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "8d9a221e-53f8-4910-8665-633446b369ee",
                                                                "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                                "amount": "1",
                                                                "change": "1",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "5615cdf5-1975-4363-81f4-43a987ed1513",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                    "text": "Someone had to stop the thief and bring him to justice after all the thefts he made... After all, whatever would the Headmaster do without his stolen hat? Some crimes cannot be born.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "6fdafc89-77fb-410d-a24c-4473d38e09b9",
                                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Because the Headmaster's hat has been returned, Mr. Terk will not be able to convince the Headmaster to shut down the Disbarred Bards class. I would say that justice has been served.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "2",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                                    "Unique": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                "scope": "actor",
                                "scopeId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                "tags": "fkwirkcaught",
                                "has": true
                            },
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "c8f53fab-2eb0-477d-a5e7-da7e5309e724",
                            "text": "Flirt With Moira",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6d5c6d0b-dcb6-4039-a706-7808e6d7a5de",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Maybe you and I could spend a little time together doing something you like to do.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9c2618ec-c927-4d9e-8f4c-34a26b2686d5",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That sounds like a fine idea...",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                                    "sections": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": {
                                                "type": "expressions.or",
                                                "left": {
                                                    "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                                    "scope": "actor",
                                                    "scopeId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                    "tags": "firstaidelective1",
                                                    "has": true
                                                },
                                                "right": {
                                                    "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                                    "scope": "actor",
                                                    "scopeId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                    "tags": "firstaidelective2",
                                                    "has": true
                                                }
                                            },
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "d12ebc63-5c2b-4f5c-9e08-232ec937a70f",
                                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "I can teach you some new First Aid techniques in the next class session.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": {
                                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                                "scope": "actor",
                                                "scopeId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                "tags": "hadfa1",
                                                "has": false
                                            },
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "286e4ae5-2570-4e6e-a579-322e1f43e8f4",
                                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Sign up for the First Aid class elective and I can teach you how to heal yourself and make bandages. I really like teaching people to take care of themselves.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "1f5025f5-35cb-412e-929c-011b6fcef020",
                                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "You should take the second session of First Aid. I'll be happy to teach you how to make healing potions and remedies.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "c3bd3c37-416c-40fd-bfd7-5c88a29249b8",
                            "text": "Goodbye",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                                    "sections": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
